{"tid":801121,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"見到好多人都話減脂期會成日好肚餓，但點解我無...","createTime":"2018-08-31T11:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T13:12:08.000Z","uid":141237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b94bcb2f0956221c5f95010abdbb07304604d56","tid":801121,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"我自己減脂需要食1800g以下，咁我平時會再低d都係keep住1400-1600g左右。<br />\n<br />\n成日見人話減脂期食得太少嘢會好肚餓，但點解我食少到even 1500g熱量都唔會覺得有咩飢餓感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一般一日3-4餐，依排假期懶遲起身一般都係12點左近食早餐，有時mix埋午餐一齊食。<br />\n跟住3-4點一餐，<br />\n7-8點一餐，<br />\n10點左右再食少少碳水+蛋白質。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我每星期都做3-5日gym，平均每次都90mins up，有時心情好仲跑埋步，雖然做完有時都會好餓，但係即刻飲返奶粉+食個飽就ok。<br />\n<br />\n有無人好似我咁覺得減脂期完全唔會覺得有餓既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣搞到我反而有d驚係咪其實食得太多...<br />\n<br />\nps：4號開始減，差不多快一個月。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打們分享下..."},{"pid":"4f78eb09edc86886af16347fb2d529c8bf26a8f4","tid":801121,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"share下自己平時食到既營養<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191827_fd5d14ae8c5fbab2c1c3ab2524afb7a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191827_fd5d14ae8c5fbab2c1c3ab2524afb7a1.png&h=81992b14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191827_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191827_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png&h=0be14f86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191828_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191828_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png&h=d36c2a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191828_b11474d460eda059905ae99399dcc60e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191828_b11474d460eda059905ae99399dcc60e.png&h=cf90076f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有部分食物計唔到落去，平均熱量攝取都係1500g左右"},{"pid":"4179e34f68bc61871b3c85e53e2baa56d725cf17","tid":801121,"uid":205034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"你夜晚食野都減到脂？仲要食包<br />\n師兄你有效嗎？"},{"pid":"f7816e99ab9856d83fb4c73a0e0d93975a534887","tid":801121,"uid":141237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4179e34f68bc61871b3c85e53e2baa56d725cf17","tid":801121,"uid":205034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"你夜晚食野都減到脂？仲要食包<br />\n師兄你有效嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"我無點check過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係夜晚食嘢關係影響不大不是嗎？<br />\n只要你一日入面攝取夠營養跟熱量就可以了吧...<br />\n同埋因為我係大概凌晨3點先開始計24小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假期搞到我習慣變勁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但不過我維持體重成2100g左右，我依家先食1500g，其實唔洗點check都一定瘦到啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d982af8946ac5e03b346f56fc325e02a567c50","tid":801121,"uid":173456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f78eb09edc86886af16347fb2d529c8bf26a8f4","tid":801121,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"share下自己平時食到既營養<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191827_fd5d14ae8c5fbab2c1c3ab2524afb7a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191827_fd5d14ae8c5fbab2c1c3ab2524afb7a1.png&h=81992b14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191827_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191827_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png&h=0be14f86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191828_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191828_cfb09f0c324c6ab88e2630d58ebbfd78.png&h=d36c2a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/191828_b11474d460eda059905ae99399dcc60e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F191828_b11474d460eda059905ae99399dcc60e.png&h=cf90076f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有部分食物計唔到落去，平均熱量攝取都係1500g左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"咩app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ff9974187eb65770a1c44f223b9eabca6b0e5b","tid":801121,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4179e34f68bc61871b3c85e53e2baa56d725cf17","tid":801121,"uid":205034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"你夜晚食野都減到脂？仲要食包<br />\n師兄你有效嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"不如你講下點解夜晚食包就減唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc44b6de4f0d3b139f0b37b63a2c3278f2c36f3","tid":801121,"uid":87563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"咩app"},{"pid":"cb45ec9bc7f21ab68f6feda8790172ade1058dc3","tid":801121,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16d982af8946ac5e03b346f56fc325e02a567c50","tid":801121,"uid":173456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":